name: Space traveler Ld43
description:
In this game, you play as a commander of a space ship. You got a very powerful ship, however, space traveling requires a lot of power. Sometimes you have to sacrifice part of function to support next fly.

How to play:

Rules: To start, you need at least energy. Launching and landing each would cost 50% energy. if You now don’t have enough energy to fly to next station, Sacrifices must be made! You can sacrifice other parts’ energy to charge the tank.

Control: Move: A,W,D,S key Shoot: SPACE Bar

Weapon: how powerful the weapon is. Catcher: how much energy you can gain each time. Control: how easily the ship turning
